    "We conducted orientation meetings with graders and observed initial assessments to help ensure consistent understanding and application of the rubrics.",
    "Using the original paper and underlying documentation, each tool was assessed by two experts using the predefined rubric criteria, who were also welcome to review additional literature that references the given tool, and did so, in some cases.",
    "Graders independently reached agreement in most cases on tool grades.",
    "Where disagreements occurred, the project team reviewed rationales and evidence, resolving differences stemming from rubric interpretation or evidence evaluation through careful analysis of the published material.",
